snippet.title: Thrilling medieval thief experience VR game [ROGAN: The Thief in the Castle]
snippet.description:
[ROGAN: The Thief in the Castle] turns its players to a thief, who should survive in the castle. 
Players will not only pickpocket and steal, but also will hide, throw materials and ambush to make their way through hardships. 

#ROGAN #ACTIONADVENTURE #VR
